{"word":"τάχος","slug":"τάχος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>τάχος, ους, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ταχύς\">ταχύς</a></el>] ‘swiftness’; in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> always in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> phrase <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> τάχει</el> (= <el>τάχεως</el>)<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on action <b>speedily, quickly, without delay <a href='B:510 10:33'>Ac 10:33</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 12:7'>12:7</a>; <a href='B:510 17:15'>17:15</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 22:18'>22:18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on time <b>soon, in a short time <a href='B:490 18:8'>Lk 18:8</a>; <a href='B:520 16:20'>Ro 16:20</a>; <a href='B:610 3:14'>1 Ti 3:14</a>; <a href='B:730 1:1'>Rv 1:1</a>; <a href='B:730 22:6'>22:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:τάχιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ταχύς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}